{"tid":816163,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Henry Cavill唔做DCEU超人","createTime":"2018-09-12T14:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T10:41:38.000Z","uid":33869,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"951aab089b5e1f1dc1b5178e89136988066c20ba","tid":816163,"uid":33869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T14:23:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cbr.com/henry-cavill-exits-superman/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbr.com%2Fhenry-cavill-exits-superman%2F&d=rh%2BHFq2FQXlGCcylTWqDIROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=1dd54919\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbr.com/henry-cavill-exits-superman/</a><br />\n<br />\nAccording to The Hollywood Reporter, Warner Bros. had sought to sign the actor for a long-rumored cameo in Shazam! However, sources indicate that negotiations broke down, pointing to the end of Cavill&rsquo;s time in the iconic red cape.<br />\n<br />\nThe reason for the negotiations impasse isn&rsquo;t clear, with THR citing one Warner Bros. source as saying it came down to a scheduling conflict &mdash; after all, Cavill did just sign on to Netflix&rsquo;s The Witcher &mdash; while another implied it may have come down to the studio&rsquo;s desire to chart another course for its DC films after a rocky start."},{"pid":"d9b89e0bcc6690df6f09849970341fcab3dff132","tid":816163,"uid":191041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T14:27:24.000Z","msg":"堅唔堅㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17708d9aef08413b8a60ca87fed9a97663353464","tid":816163,"uid":140454,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"拍傑佬份份鐘紅過拍底褲佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80135e1ff90c63833b23c036d7ee05a2c18dbcf6","tid":816163,"uid":100236,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T14:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/201